1. To Create War file using a profile(say, dev)
	*mvn clean package -P dev
	/*  this will create a war file as 'filename.war' as  specified in the <fileName> section of the pom.xml*/
    /*	for the mentioned profile(eg:dev)*/

2. To Deploy war file to the server from terminal using the profile (say, dev)
	*mvn clean tomcat7:redeploy -P dev
	/* this will deploy or redeploy the 'filename.war' file to the server given in the pom.xml, */
	/* for the mentioned profile(say, dev)*/
